#: jetpack_vendor/automattic/jetpack-backup/src/abilities/class-backup-abilities.php:170
msgid "Return a single-call snapshot of the site backup state: { last_backup, recent_backup_count, schedule, storage }. Use this to answer \"is my site protected?\" before deciding whether to call list-backups, list-restores, or request-backup. Read-only and idempotent. Fields whose backing service is unreachable come back as null rather than failing the call. Requires the manage_options capability."
